# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:72
msgid "Start Frame"
msgstr "Frame Awal"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:72
msgid "The first frame to export (default is 1)"
msgstr "Frame pertama yang akan diekspor (default adalah 1)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:73
msgid "End Frame"
msgstr "Frame Akhir"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:73
msgid ""
"The final frame to export (default is the last frame in your project to "
"contain a clip)"
msgstr ""
"Frame terakhir yang akan diekspor (default adalah frame terakhir dalam "
"proyek Anda yang berisi klip)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:74
msgid "Start at First Clip"
msgstr "Mulai dari Klip Pertama"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:74
msgid ""
"This checkbox will toggle the **Start Frame** between `0.0` and the `start` "
"of the first clip/transition position."
msgstr ""
"Kotak centang ini akan mengalihkan **Start Frame** antara `0.0` dan `awal` "
"posisi klip/transisi pertama."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:75
msgid "End at Last Clip"
msgstr "Akhiri di Klip Terakhir"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:75
msgid ""
"This checkbox will toggle the **End Frame** between the `end` of the "
"furthest clip/transition and the full `project duration`. The project "
"duration can be adjusted by dragging the right edge of any track. You will "
"need to zoom out (:guilabel:`Ctrl+Scroll Wheel`) of the timeline before you "
"can drag the right edge of a track."
msgstr ""
"Kotak centang ini akan mengalihkan **End Frame** antara `akhir` klip/"
"transisi terjauh dan `durasi proyek` penuh. Durasi proyek dapat disesuaikan "
"dengan menyeret tepi kanan dari trek mana pun. Anda perlu memperkecil "
"tampilan (:guilabel:`Ctrl+Scroll Wheel`) timeline sebelum dapat menyeret "
"tepi kanan trek."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:81
msgid ""
"A video profile is a collection of common video settings (*size, frame rate, "
"aspect ratio*). Profiles are used during editing, previewing, and exporting "
"to provide a quick way to switch between common combinations of these "
"settings. The :guilabel:`Export Dialog` will **default** to the same profile "
"used by the project."
msgstr ""
"Profil video adalah kumpulan pengaturan video umum (*ukuran, frame rate, "
"rasio aspek*). Profil digunakan selama pengeditan, pratinjau, dan ekspor "
"untuk memberikan cara cepat beralih antara kombinasi umum pengaturan ini. :"
"guilabel:`Export Dialog` akan **default** menggunakan profil yang sama "
"dengan yang digunakan oleh proyek."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:85
msgid ""
"*NOTE: It is important to choose a **Profile** with the same **aspect "
"ratio** used when editing your project. If you are exporting at a "
"**different aspect ratio**, it might stretch the image, crop the image, add "
"black bars, or otherwise introduce an issue which changes the exported "
"video, making it appear differently than the :guilabel:`Preview` inside "
"OpenShot.*"
msgstr ""
"*CATATAN: Penting untuk memilih **Profil** dengan **rasio aspek** yang sama "
"saat mengedit proyek Anda. Jika Anda mengekspor dengan **rasio aspek "
"berbeda**, ini mungkin meregangkan gambar, memotong gambar, menambahkan "
"bilah hitam, atau menyebabkan masalah lain yang mengubah video yang "
"diekspor, sehingga tampilannya berbeda dari :guilabel:`Preview` di dalam "
"OpenShot.*"

